<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-discovery-could-mean-better-access-to-more-donor-hearts-and-improved-transplant-outcomes/">Mayo Clinic discovery could mean better access to more donor hearts and improved transplant outcomes</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
