		<title>Construction worker rapidly loses ability to walk &amp;#8211; Mayo Clinic researchers discover the cause</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/construction-worker-rapidly-loses-ability-to-walk-mayo-clinic-researchers-discover-the-cause/</link>
		
